M|Core|tx|1. **Composition over cfg** — Instead of adding props, let consumers
M|Core|tx|compose
M|Core|tx|2. **Lift your state** — State in pr, not trapped in cp
M|Core|tx|3. **Compose your internals** — Subcomponents access context, not props
M|Core|tx|4. **Explicit variants** — cr ThreadComposer, EditComposer, not Composer
